examples.en: He recommended her without any reservations.
I had serious reservations about his appointment as captain.
The USA expressed reservations before agreeing to sign the agreement.
The restaurant totally goofed up our reservations.
Customers are advised to make seat reservations well in advance.
An online tutorial gives basic instructions for those who have never made reservations on the Web.
We made dinner reservations at the restaurant for 6 o'clock.
